721
00:35:50,230 --> 00:35:51,480
I...

722
00:35:52,179 --> 00:35:54,928
was promised
move-in ready.

723
00:35:58,112 --> 00:36:01,005
Mm.
Mm.

724
00:36:01,150 --> 00:36:02,820
- Hey.
- Hi.

725
00:36:04,512 --> 00:36:07,902
Welcome home.
Oh.

726
00:36:09,275 --> 00:36:13,335
♪ Footprints in the sand
remind us that we can ♪

727
00:36:13,455 --> 00:36:14,912
How was your day?

728
00:36:15,101 --> 00:36:17,210
Yeah, it was...
It was pretty okay.

729
00:36:17,268 --> 00:36:18,452
- Yeah?
- Mm-hmm.

730
00:36:18,510 --> 00:36:21,070
You raised a great kid.

731
00:36:21,128 --> 00:36:23,702
♪ Light, it turns to dust ♪

732
00:36:23,776 --> 00:36:25,283
♪ And leaves because
it must evaporate ♪

733
00:36:25,340 --> 00:36:26,913
Thanks.

734
00:36:28,818 --> 00:36:30,296
Where's Owen?

735
00:36:30,798 --> 00:36:33,218
I dropped him off
at the airport.

736
00:36:33,307 --> 00:36:35,296
He said
he'll come visit soon.

